SCREWED UP THAT KID.

48:18.520 --> 48:21.683
JUST LIKE YOU AND LISA
ARE GONNA SCREW UP MAYA.

48:21.790 --> 48:23.189
FUCK YOU.

48:23.300 --> 48:24.324
