TO STAY IN THIS

48:24.430 --> 48:26.159
TO PROVE WHAT A GOOD GUY
YOU CAN BE.

48:26.270 --> 48:27.965
NOT BECAUSE
YOU LOVE LISA.

48:28.070 --> 48:29.799
