YEAH.

48:38.010 --> 48:40.945
WELL, WHO ISN'T ?

48:41.050 --> 48:43.314
THE ONLY WAY NOT TO BE TRAPPED
IS TO NOT HAVE ANYTHING.

48:43.420 --> 48:45.445
YOU LOOK ME IN THE EYE
AND TELL ME THAT

48:45.550 --> 48:47.518
SOMETIMES YOU DON'T WANT
TO GET IN YOUR CAR

48:47.620 --> 48:49.815
AND JUST
START DRIVING

48:49.920 --> 48:52.320
AND NEVER LOOK BACK.

48:52.430 --> 48:54.728
